    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Astyanax pirapuan, holotype, undetermined sex, MNRJ 37621, 45.4 mm SL, Brazil, Mato Grosso, Chapada dos Guimarães, Rio Aricá-Mirim, Rio Cuiabá basin." ;
