<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205130>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Astyanax pirapuan, paratype, LBP 5662, 54.3 mm SL. Upper and lower jaws, left lateral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
