    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205131>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Area showing sites of occurrence of Astyanax pirapuran (Brazil, Mato Grosso State, Chapada dos Guimarães, Rio Aricá-mirim, Rio Cuiabá basin, 1543 ’ 11 ” S 5527 ’ 18 ” W). Star: type locality, white circle: paratypes, square: Cuiabá, MT." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205131/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

